query:
SELECT
            rr.id,
            rr.payload,
            rr.certificates,
            rr.signature,
            rr.created_at
        FROM
            objects AS rr
        WHERE
            rr.object_type = $1
          AND
            NOT EXISTS (
                SELECT 1
                FROM objects AS r
                WHERE r.object_type = $2
                  AND rr.id = (convert_from(r.payload, 'UTF8')::jsonb ->> $3)::uuid
            )
        ORDER BY rr.created_at DESC
